#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:49
msgid "Shader"
msgstr "着色器"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:49
msgid ""
"The value as delivered by the material's shader (*Lambert*, *Cook Torrance*) "
"defines the color. Here the amount of light does not matter for color, only "
"the direction of the light."
msgstr ""
"与材质的着色器(*兰伯特* 、 *库克 托伦斯*)一样，该值用于定义颜色，这种情况下，"
"只有光线的方向影响颜色，光线的数量不影响。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:52
msgid "Energy"
msgstr "能量"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:52
msgid ""
"As *Shader*, now also lamp energy, color, and distance are taken into "
"account. This makes the material change color when more light shines on it."
msgstr ""
"与 *着色器* 一样，不过现在将光源能量、颜色和距离考虑在内。这使得当增加照射到材"
"质表面的光线时，材质颜色随之发生变化。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:55
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "法线"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:55
msgid ""
"The surface normal, relative to the camera, is used for the *Ramp Shader*. "
"This is possible with a texture as well, but added for convenience."
msgstr ""
"将相对相机的表面法向用于 *渐变着色器* 。这也可以使用贴图实现，不过为了方便还是"
"加入了该选项。"

